originalText.text: If I can give this place negative 10 star I would. I already had my prepaid reservation when I got there there was no issue the issue came when we were about to leave. The attendant came over and said to me that there was a balance due and I asked him why, then he replied oh you went over the time which it was not true and I had showed him the time we were actually very early and he came up and said oh your vehicle is oversized which is not my vehicle was a GLE coupe is a regular size car. Any how we feel we were hustle and robbed right in our face we will report this Business to the better business bureau because this is not fair to consumers. Is not about the money is about people trying to hustle you I don’t appreciate that and that’s not good way of doing business
